headline.main: JAPANESE IN FEUD WITH HIRELING ARMY; Chinese Mercenaries Defy Wang -- Yingshan Falls to Foe

lead_paragraph: CHUNGKING, China, Dec. 31 (AP) -- Friction between the Japanese and a Chinese hireling army near Peiping, in which the mediation efforts of Japan's puppet premier, Wang Ching-Wei, have failed, was reported by a Chinese communique today.
